              <li><a href="https://www.cityofkingston.ca/bylaws-and-animal-services/bylaw-enforcement/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bylaw Enforcement</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>Bylaws can change. The information here reflects Bylaw 2021-10 as amended through September 2024, but always check the city's website for the most current version.</p>

